(1, 'Bangladesh Sweden Polytechnic Institute (BSPI) is one of the famous and well reputed technical educational institute in Bangladesh. It was established at Kaptai under Rangamati Hill Tracts in 1963 with the help of Sweden Government. The total campus area is 30.5 acre. BSPI is one of the Government institutes under ministry of education through Directorate of technical education while the academic program is controlled by the Bangladesh Technical Education Board (BTEB). It offers 4-years (8 Semester) Diploma-in-Engineering courses.', '<p><strong>Bangladesh Sweden Polytechnic Institute</strong> (<strong>BSPI</strong>) is one of the famous and well reputed technical educational institute in Bangladesh. It was established at Kaptai under Rangamati Hill Tracts in 1963 with the help of Sweden Government. The total campus area is 30.5 acre. BSPI is one of the Government institutes under ministry of education through Directorate of technical education while the academic program is controlled by the Bangladesh Technical Education Board (BTEB). It offers 4-years (8 Semester) Diploma-in-Engineering courses.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>There are six Institutes in this institute. Now the total picture of the Departments and its respective seat capacities with 4 years courseare:(as on 2015)</p>\r\n\r\n<table align="center" border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td rowspan="2" style="width:43px">\r\n			<p><strong>SL</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td rowspan="2" style="width:106px">\r\n			<p>Name of the Department</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td colspan="3" style="width:319px">\r\n			<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td rowspan="2" style="width:106px">\r\n			<p>Year of Establish</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="width:106px">\r\n			<p><strong>1ST SHIFT</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width:106px">\r\n			<p><strong>2ND SHIFT</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width:106px">\r\n			<p><strong>TOTAL</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="width:43px">\r\n			<p><strong>1</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width:106px">\r\n			<p><strong>Automobile</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width:106px">\r\n			<p><strong>30</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width:106px">\r\n			<p><strong>30</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width:106px">\r\n			<p><strong>60</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width:106px">\r\n			<p><strong>1965</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="width:43px">\r\n			<p><strong>2</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width:106px">\r\n			<p><strong>Civil(Wood)</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width:106px">\r\n			<p><strong>30</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width:106px">\r\n			<p><strong>30</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width:106px">\r\n			<p><strong>60</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width:106px">\r\n			<p><strong>2001</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="width:43px">\r\n			<p><strong>3</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width:106px">\r\n			<p><strong>Computer</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width:106px">\r\n			<p><strong>60</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width:106px">\r\n			<p><strong>60</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width:106px">\r\n			<p><strong>120</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width:106px">\r\n			<p><strong>2002</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="width:43px">\r\n			<p><strong>4</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width:106px">\r\n			<p><strong>Construction</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width:106px">\r\n			<p><strong>60</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width:106px">\r\n			<p><strong>60</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width:106px">\r\n			<p><strong>120</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width:106px">\r\n			<p><strong>2006</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="width:43px">\r\n			<p><strong>5</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width:106px">\r\n			<p><strong>Electrical</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width:106px">\r\n			<p><strong>30</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width:106px">\r\n			<p><strong>30</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width:106px">\r\n			<p><strong>60</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width:106px">\r\n			<p><strong>1964</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="width:43px">\r\n			<p><strong>6</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width:106px">\r\n			<p><strong>Mechanical</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width:106px">\r\n			<p><strong>30</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width:106px">\r\n			<p><strong>30</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width:106px">\r\n			<p><strong>60</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width:106px">\r\n			<p><strong>1964</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>History&amp; Background</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>It was established in 1963 by the initiative of Swedish Government as Swedish-Pakistan Institute of Technology. After emergence of Bangladesh, the institute renamed as Bangladesh Sweden Polytechnic Institute. BSPI is now one of the distinguished and well-reputed technical educational institutes in Bangladesh. It has qualified teachers,workshops and laboratories with modern equipments. About 1500 students are now studying in different technical fields of this institute.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Buildings:-</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Institute buildings includes-</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>(a) One single storey structure for workshop for Civil- Wood Technology.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>(b) One double storey structure being used for science laboratory and class rooms,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>(c) One double storey structure for office accommodation.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>(d) One single storey structure for the workshops of Automobile, Electrical and Mechanical Technologies.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>(e) One single storey structure for canteen.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>(f) One double storey and one 3 storey structure for students Hostel and one 4 storey structure for female Hostel</p>\r\n\r\n<p>(g) One 4 storey structure (newly build) for Computer and Construction Technology.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>(h) One wood seasoning chambers and impregnation plant.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>(i) 2 blocks of garages and Electric Sub-station.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>(j) One covered walkway linking all the buildings.</p>\r\n');

